These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, go, poker
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
3. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
5. the person playing snooker is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Game   | go | poker      | snooker | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, italian, malaysian
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, train, skateboard
1. the egyptian is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the skateboard##2
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian | egyptian   | australian |
| Transport           | train      | motorbike    | bus | skateboard      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, mah-jongg, poker
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, quad-bike, train
1. the person playing bridge is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
5. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
6. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Game        | bridge | scrabble | mah-jongg     | poker |
| Transport   | car  | train   | quad-bike | bus    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, golf, swimming, skiing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, epic, family, romance
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
5. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Sport         | swimming | tennis | golf | skiing |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | family     | epic    | crime       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, coffee, tea
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking water##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | tea | water | coffee |

