.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, light-blue, blood-red, grey
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, russian, thai, turkish
1. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the turkish is between the person who likes grey and the thai##2
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Color           | blue | light-blue | grey | blood-red |
| Nationality   | thai        | turkish     | japanese       | russian   |

