.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz, salsa
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, woodworking, writing
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of ambient is between the fan of hip-hop and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
3. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
5. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
6. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient  | jazz  | salsa   |
| Hobby           | writing  | camping | woodworking | filmmaking |

