.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, milk
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, snooker, billiard
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
5. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
6. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| Game       | mah-jongg       | snooker   | billiard | monopoly |

