.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
House: cape-cod, modern, tower, art-deco
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the modern house##3
2. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
5. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda       | cola   | tea        |
| House      | modern  | art-deco | cape-cod | tower |

