.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, fishing, sudoku
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, onion, avocado, pineapple
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
2. the person eating avocado is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person eating avocado##5
5. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person eating nectarine##5
6. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person eating nectarine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | board-games | drawing   | fishing | sudoku     |
| Food   | onion     | nectarine | avocado  | pineapple |

