.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, chess, collecting, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, lacrosse, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
4. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Hobby   | camping | collecting        | sudoku        | chess |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | skateboarding | basketball | golf |

