.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, woodworking, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, romance, time-travel, epic
1. the person watching romance movies is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
3. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing | dancing | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | epic  | romance  | time-travel    |

