.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, thriller, western
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, blend, dannemann, dunhill
1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
3. the blend-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
6. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | disaster | documentary | thriller |
| Cigar   | dannemann | alhambra | blend   | dunhill  |

