1. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
2. the thai is the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes white##1
4. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the german##5
5. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | german     | italian | turkish | thai |
| Color     | white | mauve    | turquise    | blood-red |

