.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, videographer, dressmaker, engineer
1. the dressmaker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the analyst is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
3. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the analyst is on the left of the videographer##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Job   | dressmaker | engineer  | analyst | videographer        |

